name: Stripped
overview: People's relationships with their personal belongings are exposed as they forego everything they own - clothing, furniture, money and all coveted possessions - for 21 days.

episodes.name: Ali & Justin
episodes.overview: Ali and her husband Justin, an unlikely Los Angeles couple who has accumulated close to 10,000 items in their home, agree to this 21-day experience hoping to assess and adjust their priorities. A career-driven fashion stylist, with a penchant for all things designer, Ali is often at odds with the more frugal Justin, an accountant with his sights set on growing their family. Now free from distraction and more vulnerable than ever, they are left to focus on each other and contemplate their future.

episodes.name: Farah, Beth & Isabel
episodes.overview: Three best friends all in their 30s are living a free-spirited Hollywood lifestyle while still chasing their respective dreams. They choose to give up all their possessions hoping to bond through a challenging experience but along they way they discover surprising things about themselves, their career paths and their relationships with each other.

episodes.name: Ariana & Ryan
episodes.overview: Fitness model, Ariana, and her school teacher boyfriend, Ryan, have their relationship put to an intense test. In the end, they must decide if their bond is strong enough to make it.

episodes.name: Autianna & Jaseena
episodes.overview: Two single sisters, Autianna and Jaseena-who share an apartment, a bartending job and frivolous spending habits-need a major wake up call. Will these sisters discover what it takes to become responsible adults?

episodes.name: Rai & Patty
episodes.overview: Rai and Patty, a newly married couple from different backgrounds, learn just how strong their bond is when they relinquish all material possessions.

episodes.name: Russ & Ariel
episodes.overview: A single ladiesâ€™ man and his recently-divorced roommate are pushed to their breaking points when they are left with an empty house and a sick pet cat. Tempers flare as these two learn to cope with sharing their living space in ways they never expected and find surprising spiritual growth along the way.

episodes.name: Brian & Jason
episodes.overview: Brian and Jason, who have been together 15 years, hope that giving up all they own will help them re-connect and finally set a wedding a date.
